{"title":"割麦子的日子","authors":["贾卫国"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":7,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"割麦子的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贾卫国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我蹒跚的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如麦地葱绿的苗苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽开母亲的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天热起来的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的脚步沉了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那开满小花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长满碧草的田埂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出一条如她额头皱纹般"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晰的小径"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我一次次禁不住闪动眸子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"审视母亲和母亲那把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨了又磨的镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割麦子的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳挂满金色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的背影也如镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿梭于熟透的麦地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小径延伸着收割的田垄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使她每每走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都和阳光一样兴奋"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}